## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="9620c-126">因為所有的類別，衍生自<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject>包含<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.NodeType%2A>屬性，您可以撰寫程式碼的運作方式的具體子類別集合<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9620c-126">Because all classes that derive from <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject> contain a <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.NodeType%2A> property, you can write code that operates on collections of concrete subclass of <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9620c-127">集合中每個節點的節點類型可以然後測試您的程式碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9620c-127">Your code can then test for the node type of each node in the collection.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="9620c-128">下列範例會建立 XML 樹狀結構，其中包含數種類型的節點。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9620c-128">The following example creates an XML tree that contains a number of types of nodes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9620c-129">它接著逐一查看樹狀目錄中，輸出每個節點的節點型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9620c-129">It then iterates through the tree, outputting the node type of each node.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9620c-130">請注意，`Child2`包含<xref:System.Xml.Linq.XText>節點，以隱含方式轉換從 字串內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9620c-130">Note that `Child2` contains an <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XText> node, implicitly converted from the string content.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Note that XNode uses XmlNodeType, which is in the System.Xml namespace.  
XDocument xmlTree = new XDocument(  
    new XComment("a comment"),  
    new XProcessingInstruction("xml-stylesheet", "type=\"text/xsl\" href=\"hello.xsl\""),  
    new XElement("Root",  
        new XAttribute("Att", "attContent"),  
        new XElement("Child1",  
            new XCData("CDATA content")  
        ),  
        new XElement("Child2", "Text content")  
    )  
);  
  
foreach (XNode node in xmlTree.DescendantNodes())  
{  
    Console.WriteLine(node.NodeType);  
    if (node.NodeType == XmlNodeType.Element)  
    {  
        foreach (XAttribute att in ((XElement)node).Attributes())  
            Console.WriteLine(att.NodeType);  
    }  
}  
```  
  
